    <string name="info_page_credits">Credits</string>
    <string name="info_about_body1">OpenVibble is a companion app for the Claude Desktop Buddy hardware setup.</string>
    <string name="info_about_body2">The top shows BLE status, the middle shows your pixel pet, and the bottom simulates A/B hardware buttons.</string>
    <string name="info_about_body3">When Claude Desktop requests permission, A approves and B denies.</string>
    <string name="info_about_body4">Source code is MPL-2.0; see GitHub for details.</string>
    <string name="info_buttons_body1">A · short press: cycle NORMAL → PET → INFO.</string>
    <string name="info_buttons_body2">A · short press · NORMAL with prompt: approve once.</string>
    <string name="info_buttons_body3">A · long press: toggle device menu.</string>
    <string name="info_buttons_body4">B · short press · NORMAL with prompt: deny.</string>
    <string name="info_buttons_body5">B · short press · PET/INFO: flip page. Horizontal swipes work too.</string>
    <string name="info_credits_body1">Claude is an Anthropic product; this project is not affiliated with Anthropic.</string>
    <string name="info_credits_body2">ASCII sprites are adapted from Kenney ASCII pet kit.</string>
    <string name="info_credits_body3">Thanks to everyone who has shared feedback in issues.</string>
